    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "6a4fefac-5199-40bc-b4d8-9a622fe7756c",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Party Crasher - An unlikely Avenger",
        "Location": "LOCATION_NORTHAMERICA",
        "PublicId": "122964632021",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/skunk/scene_skunk.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 7271eae1-6bdd-4936-b763-b2390fb07fe7).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47. Today&apos;s contract came from an unusual client, a young IT prodigy. Known be smart way over of his age, even at such a young age. His quiet and antisocial behavior has often caused people to single him out from their groups, yet this is not what led to him contacting us.  3 months ago, a group of fresh high-school graduates, bullied one of his few best friends into committing suicide. Leading him to contacting us, seeking to crash their graduation party... and to send a message.",
